Page Description
1.Home page (index.html)
.Welcome message and introduction
.Overview of features
.Link to all other pages
.Location highlight: Mention that it’s based in Bharapur-7, Buddhachowk.
.Explore Library and Shop Books

2. About Us
Introduction: Book Sansar is both a library and a bookstore, serving readers in Buddhachowk.
#Vision:
.Promote reading culture in Nepal.
.Provide affordable access to books of all genres.
.Blend traditional library services with modern online shopping.

#Why Choose Us:
.Wide collection of books.
.Comfortable reading space.
.Easy online browsing and purchasing.
.Community-driven events and friendly staff.

3.product
#Book Categories:
.Fiction (novels, thrillers, classics).
.Non-Fiction (biographies, self-help, history, science).
.Academic (textbooks, references, exam guides).
.Children’s Books (storybooks, comics, educational).

# Platform Features:
.Smart search by title, author, or genre.
.Preview sample chapters before buying.
.Secure checkout and fast delivery.
.Discounts for students and members.

